{"tid":1714572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[問下呀媽情況]糧食供應鏈是否妥當。避免被用作彈藥","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T02:04:29.000Z","uid":102343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67ef58174459a83840077a42cf6e46137fbe6b1f","tid":1714572,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:58:43.000Z","msg":"民以食為天，如果長時間多處堵路，物流會收到影響。<br />\n<br />\n當補唔到貨時，社區沒有足夠食物供應，可能會被狗政府用作人血饅頭攻擊我地。人無得食野真係可以做到好痴線嘅野，除非我地可以將矛頭指向政府，唔係嘅話一定要小心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但放路我地就冇左效果。<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法防止呢個情況發生?<br />\n國際援助?<br />\n聯絡超市、街市了解物流，短暫放路?<br />\n人鏈傳貨、全民苦力?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益"},{"pid":"4511db30a307ee07cecec02f489107c2aabd574d","tid":1714572,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"f20c026e1df26c1066cf4ebb8258e370f1c451cd","tid":1714572,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"1ae91ae58b20987c5c138d41c8d42da10bbb6bcc","tid":1714572,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:03:40.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"39ec0af6bfc5132ec35ed79e9a49ad10d2351eb3","tid":1714572,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"定係無視個擔憂，實行真攬炒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祈望全民缺糧正式破斧沈舟總攻擊?"}]}